mcclain industries <mccl> sets stock split
    sterling heights, mich., march 30 - 
mcclain industries inc said its board declared a four-for-three stock
split, payable 30, record april 15. the company also said it plans to
open within the next 90 days a 114,000 square foot plant in macon,
ga., that will allow it to expand production of transfer trailers and
other products. reuter 
